name: MacVim r176.1 (prerelease)
body:
Updated to Vim 9.0.1403

* Printing files in macOS 13 Ventura is now fixed.

<small>This is a pre-release version of MacVim. To use the latest stable release, see <https://github.com/macvim-dev/macvim/releases/latest></small>

<details><summary>What's Changed</summary>

## What's Changed
* Remove Sparkle 2's XPCServices symlink by @ychin in https://github.com/macvim-dev/macvim/pull/1367
* Update gui_mac.txt headings by @dkav in https://github.com/macvim-dev/macvim/pull/1363
* Don't throw Objective C exception when quitting MacVim by @ychin in https://github.com/macvim-dev/macvim/pull/1371
* Fix Xcode 8 build breaks by @ychin in https://github.com/macvim-dev/macvim/pull/1372
* Remove Sparkle.framework when configured with --disable-sparkle by @ychin in https://github.com/macvim-dev/macvim/pull/1373
* Remove Homebrew no-auto-update env var from CI by @ychin in https://github.com/macvim-dev/macvim/pull/1374
* Fix upstream merge CI failure with 'winaltkeys' by @ychin in https://github.com/macvim-dev/macvim/pull/1376
* Clean up syntax / formatting / typos in MacVim docs by @ychin in https://github.com/macvim-dev/macvim/pull/1375
* Add security policy file / documentation by @ychin in https://github.com/macvim-dev/macvim/pull/1377
* Fix `set fullscreen` not working after upstream Vim merge by @ychin in https://github.com/macvim-dev/macvim/pull/1379
* Fix MacVim localized intro text, and don't hide the `:h version9` prompt by @ychin in https://github.com/macvim-dev/macvim/pull/1381
* Fix 'gdefault' etc help tags being broken by @ychin in https://github.com/macvim-dev/macvim/pull/1383
* Improve login shell docs by @ychin in https://github.com/macvim-dev/macvim/pull/1386
* Fix CI not handling Xcode version correctly with packages by @ychin in https://github.com/macvim-dev/macvim/pull/1387
* Fix qlstephen project warnings by @ychin in https://github.com/macvim-dev/macvim/pull/1388
* Fix MacVim CI breakage in Test_mouse_shape_after_cancelling_gr by @ychin in https://github.com/macvim-dev/macvim/pull/1392
* Fix misc MacVim project warnings in Xcode by @ychin in https://github.com/macvim-dev/macvim/pull/1391
* Fix :hardcopy not working in macOS 13 Ventura by @ychin in https://github.com/macvim-dev/macvim/pull/1390
* About MacVim show "pre-release" when running a pre-release build by @ychin in https://github.com/macvim-dev/macvim/pull/1393

## New Contributors
* @dkav made their first contribution in https://github.com/macvim-dev/macvim/pull/1363

**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/macvim-dev/macvim/compare/release-176...prerelease-176.1

</details>
